  "name": "Telekinesis",
  "type": "feature",
  "img": "icons/magic/control/energy-stream-link-blue.webp",
  "system": {
    "description": "<p>Your Telekinesis grants you the following benefits:</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Limited Telekinesis:</strong> You are able to use your mind to easily&nbsp;move objects around you.</p>\n<p>You can spend <strong>1 AP </strong>to interact with an object up to 5 lbs (2.5 kg) that is within 5 Spaces. You can manipulate objects, open doors or containers, etc.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Combat Telekinesis: </strong>You gain access to the <strong>Grapple&nbsp;Maneuvers</strong>.</p>\n<p>You can take the <strong>Grapple </strong>and <strong>Shove </strong>Actions against creatures within 5 Spaces.</p>\n<p>When you make a Check as part of a <strong>Shove Action</strong>, <strong>Grapple Action</strong>, <strong>Grapple Maneuver</strong>, or to escape a Grapple, you can make a <strong>Spell Check </strong>instead.</p>\n<p>When you use the <strong>Body Block Maneuver </strong>in this way, the target must be within 1 Space of you.</p>\n<p>When you use <strong>Throw Maneuver </strong>in this way, you use your <strong>Prime Modifier </strong>instead of your <strong>Might </strong>to determine the distance thrown. Additionally, you (p52) Throw the creature from its Space instead of your own.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong>Action Point Enhancements</strong></span></p>\n<p>You can choose to spend additional <strong>AP when </strong>you take the <strong>Shove Action </strong>or perform the <strong>Throw Maneuver </strong>but before&nbsp;making the <strong>Spell Check</strong>. You can choose multiple effects or the same effect multiple times. If you spend <strong>AP </strong>on multiple effects, the target only makes 1 Save against all effects.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Push: (1 AP)</strong> The target is Pushed up to 1 additional Space.</li>\n<li><strong>Forceful: (1 AP) </strong>The target has DisADV on their Physical Save they make.</li>\n<li><strong>Slow: (1 AP)</strong> The target becomes Slowed (every 1 Space&nbsp;they move costs an extra 1 Space of movement) until the&nbsp;end of your next turn.</li>\n<li><strong>Rend Body: (1 AP)</strong> The target&rsquo;s <strong>PD </strong>is reduced by 2 until the end of your next turn.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong>Mana Point Enhancement</strong></span></p>\n<p>You can spend 1 or more MP (up to your Combat Mastery) before you make the Spell Check to choose 2 additional AP&nbsp;Enhancements.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><em><strong>System Tip:&nbsp;</strong>Use that feature instead of rolling maneuvers and Actions. This feature is configured as a contest between your Spell Check and enemy Martial Check.</em></p>",
